            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>Dulcessimo et amavile nepote meo <persName key="#Other_clerics"
                                ><name ref="Adrebertus">Atripert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerico</rs>, ego <persName key="#Priests"><name
                                ref="Audoaldus">Adoald</name></persName> vir venerabilis <rs
                            key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>, rectore <rs key="#Churches">eclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/610">Sancti
                            Savini</orgName> loco <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/64"
                            >Asulari</placeName> abus et confermator tuus perpetuam salutem.
                        Manifeste et ispecialiter constat, eo quod ex germine meo habui dulce bone
                        memorie filio meo (…) <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Fortis"
                                >Fortes</name></persName> (…) qui iam per permissionem et
                        largitaetati demessuria domni viri beatissimi <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/343">Peredeo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et pontifex noster ad honorem <rs
                            key="#Priests">presviterii</rs> accessit, et per sagrationem <persName
                            key="#Bishops" ref="#people/706">Andree</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/66">Pisane</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitati</rs>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs>; <foreign>ora morto</foreign> Fortes
                            <foreign>ed essendo privo di altri figli</foreign>, per consilio ipsius
                        domni et viri beatissimi patri nostro Peredei episcopi simulque et
                        sacerdotium eius <foreign>conferma a</foreign> Atripert nepote meo, qui de
                        ipso Fortene filio meo genitus his, id est eclesia ipsa qui <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Private_foundations #Joint_foundations">est
                            edita</rs> in honore Deo et <orgName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Churches #Private_foundations #Joint_foundations"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/610">Sancti Savini</orgName> in suprascripto
                        loco a bone memorie <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Churches #Priests #Private_foundations #Joint_foundations"
                                ><name ref="Baroncio">Baroncione</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Churches #Private_foundations #Joint_foundations"
                                ><name ref="Ursus">Ursone</name></persName>, et ipse Baroncio me
                        inivi <rs key="#Ordinatio">per cartula confirmaverat</rs>, vel in omnia res
                        ad ipsa Dei eclesia pertinente, que inivi ad ipsos Baroncione et Ursus data
                        est <foreign>o da altri sono state donate</foreign> tam in <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casis</rs> quamque et in <rs
                            key="#Cereals">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Oil"
                            >olivetis</rs>, <rs key="#Acorns">silvis</rs>, <rs key="#Chestnuts"
                            >castanietis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis, pascuis</rs>, cultis
                        vel incultis (…) <rs key="#Slave_labour #Slave">servos et ancellas</rs>.
                            <foreign>Se ne riserva il governo e l’usufrutto. Se Atripert, morto il
                            nonno, dovesse scomparire prima di aver raggiunto la maggiore
                            età</foreign>, tam in predicta Dei eclesia quamque eidem pertinente sit
                        inivi confirmatum tu <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Theodradus"
                                >Teuderad</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> nepote meo <foreign>con le stesse
                            clausole</foreign>. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName key="#Writer"
                                ><name ref="David">David</name></persName>. (…) Actum <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs> ista <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/4">Lucense</placeName>. […]</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
